    "designIntent": "Translate the reference image into a warm, dimensional, professional CareerVivid iOS system for job search, resumes, interviews, reports, and career progress."
  },
  "principles": [
    "Use a near-white app canvas with layered white cards, soft gray shadows, and subtle borders.",
    "Use orange as the primary action and selected-state color, not as the only visual color.",
    "Make cards feel tactile with radius, shadow, and light tinted state backgrounds.",
    "Use large confident screen titles, compact section titles, and readable semibold card text.",
    "Preserve CareerVivid's calm career workspace feel; avoid a toy-like AI assistant aesthetic.",
    "Use icons as small functional anchors for tasks, reports, resumes, interviews, and profile actions.",
    "Keep mobile layouts dense enough for repeated use while still feeling breathable and premium."
  ],
